p-content/uploads/2012/04/MailChimp-320x200.jpg" class="attachment-showcase wp-post-image" alt="MailChimp" title="MailChimp" /></a><p><p>Subscribe customers to Mail Chimp Email lists during checkout.</p>\n</p><a href="https://easydigitaldownloads.com/extensions/mail-chimp/?ref=1" title="MailChimp" class="button-secondary">Get this Add On</a></div><div class="edd-extension"><h3 class="edd-extension-title">AWeber</h3><a href="https://easydigitaldownloads.com/extensions/aweber/?utm_source=plugin-addons-page&#038;utm_medium=plugin&#038;utm_campaign=EDDAddonsPage&#038;utm_content=AWeber" title="AWeber"><img width="320" height="200" src="https://easydigitaldownloads.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/AWeber-320x200.jpg" class="attachment-showcase wp-post-image" alt="AWeber" title="AWeber" /></a><p><p>Adds an option for users to sign up for your AWeber Email list during checkout.</p>\n</p><a href="https://easydigitaldownloads.com/extensions/aweber/?ref=1" title="AWeber" class="button-secondary">Get this Add On</a></div><div class="edd-extension"><h3 class="edd-extension-title">EDD Social Discounts</h3><a href="https://easydigitaldownloads.com/extensions/edd-social-discounts/?utm_source=plugin-addons-page&#038;utm_medium=plugin&#038;utm_campaign=EDDAddonsPage&#038;utm_content=EDDSocialDiscounts" title="EDD Social Discounts"><img width="320" height="200" src="https://easydigitaldownloads.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/edd-social-discounts1-320x200.png" class="attachment-showcase wp-post-image" alt="edd-social-discounts" title="EDD Social Discounts" /></a><p><p>Give special discounts to buyers that share your products out to social networks.</p>\n</p><a href="https://easydigitaldownloads.com/extensions/edd-social-discounts/?ref=1" title="EDD Social Discounts" class="button-secondary">Get this Add On</a></div><div class="edd-extension"><h3 class="edd-extension-title">PDF Invoices</h3><a href="https://easydigitaldownloads.com/extensions/pdf-invoices/?utm_source=plugin-addons-page&#